| 4.2 | Migrate Git commands: `GitCloneCommand`, `GitPushCommand`, `GitPullCommand` | [4_2/](4_2/INDEX.md) |
| 4.3 | Migrate GitHub commands: `GitHubCreateRepoCommand` and others | [4_3/](4_3/INDEX.md) |
