## Pattern Per Command
```python
# Before
qm = QueueManager()
task_id = qm.add_docker_push_task(image_name, tag)

# After
integration = get_queue_integration()
result = await integration.add_job(DockerJob, job_id, {"op": "push", "image": image_name, "tag": tag})
```

## Notes
- Migrate one domain at a time, test after each batch
- `job_id` = deterministic string, e.g. `f"docker_push_{image_name}_{tag}"`
- Return `job_id` from command so caller can poll status
